{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Rhnbr2r3vxtB4jMqJJsnyf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error says that adding the arbiter would change the implicit default write concern. This is because when you have 2 data-bearing members, the majority write concern requires both to acknowledge. Adding an arbiter changes how majority is calculated.\n\nI need to first set the default write concern explicitly, then add the arbiter. The typical fix is to set `{w: 1}` or `{w: \"majority\"}` as the default write concern before proceeding.\n\nActually, the error is because MongoDB 5.0+ requires that you explicitly set a cluster-wide default write concern before changing the replica set configuration in a way that would change the implicit default. \nSo I'll use the `setDefaultRWConcern` command to establish an explicit write concern like `{w: 1}`, then proceed with adding the arbiter.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":33108,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e395d5e0-0ed9-4f0e-a6dc-6bcf3129673e","uuid":"ab87ac0a-e4d5-4dbc-b28f-2378a4bbf988","request_id":"req_011CcMWd4RJEfi81EP56b6gZ"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Rhnbr2r3vxtB4jMqJJsnyf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MongoDB requires an explicit default write concern before adding an arbiter (since it changes the majority calculation). I'll set it then add the arbiter."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":33108,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e395d5e0-0ed9-4f0e-a6dc-6bcf3129673e","uuid":"b7efb88d-a5a5-4fd3-98dd-5f5dfc75496e","request_id":"req_011CcMWd4RJEfi81EP56b6gZ"}
